d serialize this properly.\n\nWait, actually - I just realized something. The user might be talking about a completely different issue. They said \"MPC\" not \"MCP\" in their first message - \"you cannot call MPC too.s\". This might be a typo for \"MCP tools\". But maybe they mean something else?\n\nRegardless, I've fixed two real bugs. Let me update the scratchpad, verify the tests pass, and explain what I fixed.",
